<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,447,2021]" pageId="12" pageNumber="163">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,321,772,797]" pageId="12" pageNumber="163">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Very similar to 
<taxonomicName box="[512,642,773,796]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Balacra" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="163" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inexpectata" status="sp. n.">
